Name: Masplado
About the game: A game that was inspired in bootlegs, most graphics made from scratch, and obviously, an original story, masplado is a plataform game with in total 33 levels (without counting the sub-levels) and 7 worlds the gameplay is a little complicated for those who are not so expert in games with hard levels also, the game have a big variety of enemies and backgrounds. some observations: the menu is very simple in the options screen have all the guide to how to play the game is saved automatically this game was made for teenagers and adults, it's not recommended for children (because of the dark humor jokes and minor details that are not appropriate for children)
